fields.title: Luxury Downtown Condo
fields.description: Modern 2-bedroom, 2-bath condo in the heart of downtown. Features skyline views, floor-to-ceiling windows, fitness center, and private parking.

fields.title: Charming Starter Home
fields.description: Cozy 2-bedroom, 1-bath bungalow with updated kitchen, hardwood floors, and large backyard. Perfect for first-time buyers.

fields.title: Spacious Family Home with Pool
fields.description: Beautiful 4-bedroom, 3-bath home with open concept living area, finished basement, 2-car garage, and outdoor pool with deck.

fields.title: Modern Loft Apartment
fields.description: Industrial-style loft with exposed brick, high ceilings, stainless steel appliances, and rooftop access. Great investment property.

fields.title: Country Retreat on 5 Acres
fields.description: Gorgeous 5-bedroom farmhouse with wraparound porch, barn, and pond. Perfect blend of rustic charm and modern amenities.
